    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "We use `web3@0.20.7` because that is the version that became used across all of MetaMask at one point in history. It's also the version that we used to inject into web pages as `window.web3`.\r\n\r\nWe are working on removing `web3` entirely from our codebase, and will replace it with `ethers` or some combination of `ethjs-` packages.\r\n\r\nThank you for your question! I will now close this issue.",
